{"tid":578486,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲赤貧者食回收肉 港素食者︰屍肉致癌何不食素","createTime":"2018-03-02T15:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T17:36:08.000Z","uid":92467,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"35e9ea66aea07b728978000ae80355ac0b0bc49b","tid":578486,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=9IsKvYIYVVVmJsVH0YwWuZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=8976565d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】全球有逾7.6億人處於極度貧窮，三餐不得溫飽。近日有外媒報道，菲律賓的赤貧者需以垃圾堆中的剩肉果腹，情況令人不忍卒睹。惟有推廣素食的社交專頁表示，「屍肉致癌，何不吃素」，旋即惹來網民怒轟。<br />\n<br />\n有外國媒體報道，菲律賓的貧民區流行一種叫「Pagpag」的「回收肉」，即是將從垃圾堆翻出的廚餘剩肉，經人手清洗及加工後，以熟食形式售出的「菜餚」。因價格低廉，故十分受當地貧民歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n社交專頁「香港素食」就報道發貼，表示「幾時都是吃素好」、「吃肉即是吃死屍」、「屍肉致癌」，更謂「何不吃素」，認為「製造屍肉的成本遠高過種植純素」。<br />\n<br />\n貼文發出後，惹來網民怒轟，斥其毫無愛心︰「話啲赤貧人口食屍肉致癌，喂，你把口真係賤到一個點」。有人質疑「人地（哋）屍肉飯，一客賣0.2美金（約1.5港元），你話俾（畀）我知邊間純素餐廳有邊一道菜賣得平過2蚊港紙？」<br />\n<br />\n另有網民諷謂，該素食專頁的說法為「現代版何不食肉糜」，質疑他「素口不素心」。更有人直言，「簡直影衰正常的素食者」。<br />\n<br />\n面對猛烈批評，專頁終回應指，一直以來分享資訊，是希望大家能反思「吃素與吃肉的背後真相」。專頁指「吃肉無疑是吃進毒素」，認為當地人不能作選擇，但「我們有得選擇」，勸喻大家「考慮吃長素或每天減少吃肉」。<br />\n<br />\n該專頁又澄清指，「小編沒有恥笑任何人，那是你閣下妄想」，並表示「高估了某些網民的理解能力」，最終對引起網民的曲解致歉。<br />\n<br />\n究竟是次風波是「觀點與角度」的問題，還是真相「越描越黑」？你又點睇呢？"},{"pid":"354b6bd8bef7883a9d723c621304b1f858a0467a","tid":578486,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:59:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180302/bkn-20180302180645621-0302_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180302%2Fbkn-20180302180645621-0302_00822_001.html&d=9IsKvYIYVVVmJsVH0YwWuZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=324ec593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180302/bkn-20180302180645621-0302_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4ddc0baac84497d6fafeb94fb243bd0dacd1d5bb","tid":578486,"uid":84148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:01:49.000Z","msg":"pagpag"},{"pid":"5aaefdc3ed7a07ee88fac656ca4d1741301b6a06","tid":578486,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"kfc咪有得食"},{"pid":"615db33c98e74329b15e1b112072ceb132dfafa1","tid":578486,"uid":166944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"何不食肉糜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06576a77b6e8ee85c40756e8b706c453650013d","tid":578486,"uid":140309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:10:23.000Z","msg":"喺香港食齋貴過食肉"},{"pid":"c946cfcf75be1b13d9c9de38ad29133aa284247d","tid":578486,"uid":67771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e06576a77b6e8ee85c40756e8b706c453650013d","tid":578486,"uid":140309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:10:23.000Z","msg":"喺香港食齋貴過食肉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"因為要扮番肉"},{"pid":"e51787530976f6d132f9eda13cb16e51230e55eb","tid":578486,"uid":58512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"一個耶撚 一個素食撚<br />\n最撚多戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5405097f8facac9d6edfd16dec85ec707963d039","tid":578486,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:22:44.000Z","msg":"之前好似咒人食肉早死都係依個page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbe26b12ca234c2fda6bcc081700d4b95b6bffc","tid":578486,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:25:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c8a45881e0b5a0ff43980438209c141398435cc","tid":578486,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"Stop making assholes famous."},{"pid":"c5a4b990e1152b68accf0d35548cc0d0463dab88","tid":578